Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.17,0:00:06.54,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這期的封面真是不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.84,0:00:10.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.05,0:00:13.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.05,0:00:16.39,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.97,0:00:20.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和女朋友有什麼進展了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.68,0:00:22.81,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.14,0:00:27.86,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那對你而言現在最需要的就是國王游戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.86,0:00:29.57,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外什麼都不存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.69,0:00:32.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算你這麼說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.24,0:00:35.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王游戲怎麼兩個人玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.66,0:00:37.91,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.83,0:00:39.62,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.83,0:00:41.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.33,0:00:43.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是去借助朋友的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.75,0:00:45.29,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要氣氛變得非常快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.29,0:00:48.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防守就會變得比較松懈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.59,0:00:52.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有三個很好的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.09,0:00:53.84,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.22,0:00:56.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是好朋友對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.43,0:00:59.89,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你做你想做的事是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你該做的事就只有一件了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.18,0:01:05.35,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去召集八女的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.35,0:01:08.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去和八女同學約好去她家玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.52,0:01:12.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.44,0:01:13.69,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.45,0:01:17.91,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我實在無法無視了 我就問問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.41,0:01:19.95,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個豎笛是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.41,0:01:22.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.35,0:02:58.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(850,640)\fad(300,300)}第6話  第一次的八女家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.93,0:02:57.39,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}話是那樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.67,0:02:58.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.47,0:03:00.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}要怎麼去邀請八女同學她們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.23,0:03:01.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.40,0:03:06.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你沒有在聽我說話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.11,0:03:11.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 在說什麼來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說暑假的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.62,0:03:19.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是在說暑假來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.29,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.84,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全沒有在聽嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.21,0:03:31.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說暑假要不要去哪裡玩的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.64,0:03:36.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子裡全是邀請八女同學她們的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.43,0:03:37.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有在聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.10,0:03:41.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只要是和八女同學在一起去哪裡都很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去八女想去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.27,0:03:48.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏天會不停地去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好准備哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.07,0:03:52.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}果然說到暑假就是海邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.65,0:03:54.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能只對我笑的這麼可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.24,0:03:58.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀請大家一起去玩這種事根本不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.16,0:04:03.54,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 總之要先確認能不能去八女家玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.29,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.58,0:04:11.26,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放學後能不能去八女同學家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.89,0:04:16.84,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.97,0:04:23.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 如果今天不行的話那改天也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.86,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.02,0:04:28.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.49,0:04:40.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也想邀請蘭子 寧音和我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.37,0:04:41.49,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 那不是超KY嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 八女同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 是可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.17,0:04:56.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然就不開心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去邀請蘭子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.52,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一你去邀請寧音吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.85,0:05:06.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...為什麼八女同學在生氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.86,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.36,0:05:11.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天放學後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.90,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.28,0:05:16.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子真是難懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.49,0:05:25.04,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想去八女家還是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.46,0:05:27.00,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.67,0:05:31.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要直接來我家對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.05,0:05:36.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 寧音和我的朋友似乎要先回去一趟再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.72,0:05:37.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.84,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭子也說要換了衣服再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.77,0:05:49.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家來之前只有我們兩個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.53,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.28,0:05:59.07,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家來之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.41,0:06:01.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來畢業吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.99,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.83,0:06:07.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.33,0:06:10.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.91,0:06:10.08,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}超惡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香椎同學 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在准備回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽柴同學你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡扭扭捏捏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.72,0:06:27.89,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭扭捏捏的...不要在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.89,0:06:29.39,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在等誰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等八女同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.27,0:06:35.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那這之後是要去約會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.57,0:06:41.53,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大家一起去八女家玩而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.70,0:06:42.99,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很開心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.33,0:06:50.54,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香椎同學 你不回去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.29,0:06:54.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽柴同學 我今天碰巧很閑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.42,0:06:57.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.76,0:07:02.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天碰巧很閑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.84,0:07:03.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.64,0:07:06.81,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.81,0:07:11.06,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我莫名其妙的就好像被將軍了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.60,0:07:15.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香椎同學也一起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.61,0:07:18.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽柴同學都這麼說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.86,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去也無妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回家一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下把地址發給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.03,0:07:27.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的號碼和ID
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.37,0:07:32.08,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就等你聯絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.30,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.75,0:07:41.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...一不小心把香椎同學也邀請了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.18,0:07:43.18,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.97,0:07:46.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正人多玩起來比較有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.18,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.90,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H1D2D1A&\fs35\frz342.4\move(641,306,661.571,254.571,100,507)\frx12\fry358}了解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.90,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H1D2D1A&\fs35\frz342.4\frx14\fry354\move(484,552,504,500,100,507)}交給我們的話\N大家都會幸福\N呼哈哈哈哈!\h\h
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.48,0:07:55.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.77,0:08:00.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說我叫了些相當棘手的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.70,0:08:09.62,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒有將我 看做男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我換個衣服 你等等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要換衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以偷看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.88,0:08:21.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.26,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.26,0:08:27.09,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一哪來這麼大膽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.10,0:08:33.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區偷窺 小菜一碟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.44,0:08:37.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.86,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等啦 請進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.49,0:08:44.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.11,0:08:46.49,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點進來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.95,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是八女同學的房間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.00,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與男人的房間截然不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像是在發光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.96,0:09:03.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別到處亂看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害羞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.72,0:09:05.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.97,0:09:07.89,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.43,0:09:09.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.35,0:09:11.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學在家的打扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.47,0:09:13.77,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色氣滿滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.69,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發型也是三股辮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.69,0:09:18.23,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得和平常不太一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.77,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有胸部也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.52,0:09:23.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波濤洶湧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.82,0:09:26.49,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 純一 你別看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.82,0:09:27.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.53,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.45,0:09:37.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一啊 你就這麼喜歡我的胸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.67,0:09:40.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.88,0:09:44.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你父母呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.67,0:09:45.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不在哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.93,0:09:50.93,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說白天她生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.93,0:09:54.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為我問她大家也要來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.98,0:10:02.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道說是機會嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}蠢貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.23,0:10:04.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我個蠢貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種機會並不多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.86,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.03,0:10:12.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出勇氣和她獨處就好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.16,0:10:17.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一 你要在靠近點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.31,0:10:37.14,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼進來的啊 蘭子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.31,0:10:38.81,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得我鎖門了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.23,0:10:42.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用放在老地方的鑰匙開的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.94,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你們兩個在做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.02,0:10:48.69,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在拿純一開玩笑而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.94,0:10:52.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他也沒有膽子把我怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.62,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs35}沒那膽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.95,0:10:56.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那膽子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.79,0:10:58.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}寧音放開我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.83,0:11:03.79,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話你隨時都可以摸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.80,0:11:13.30,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽柴同學 對不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走過的時候膝蓋不小心碰到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.51,0:11:18.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 為什麼這家伙也在這啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.35,0:11:25.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本城前輩 來同學的家裡玩很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.28,0:11:32.07,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明滿園春色的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.07,0:11:34.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這混亂的狀況是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.91,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去開門 你們稍等一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一的朋友們來了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.83,0:11:45.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.30,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這是什麼打扮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.30,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎平 景吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.30,0:11:53.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 很帥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了和女生玩我所准備的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}來這裡的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.05,0:11:58.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最犀利的裝備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.47,0:12:00.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}沒被人提醒簡直是奇跡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.89,0:12:04.69,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景吾就直接成了十足的壞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.69,0:12:06.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰啰嗦嗦吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.02,0:12:07.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人就該穿成這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.94,0:12:10.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來 稔是最正常...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.94,0:12:14.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼豎笛會多出一支來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.16,0:12:17.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧慎平和景吾能容忍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.20,0:12:19.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不懂你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.25,0:12:23.37,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一 你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.75,0:12:25.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.75,0:12:27.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.71,0:12:30.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是純一的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.80,0:12:32.72,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.47,0:12:38.14,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該也知道 他們是我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.18,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.85,0:12:40.72,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.47,0:12:42.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.90,0:12:49.61,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們這群人要玩什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.44,0:12:56.07,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有僅在男男女女聚會才能玩嗨的游戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.66,0:12:57.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.74,0:13:05.04,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名為 國王游戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.08,0:13:10.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能否認我中了他們的套路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.30,0:13:15.09,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但玩起游戲來 說不定防御就會變弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.51,0:13:17.93,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王游戲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.22,0:13:21.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒玩過 想試一試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.89,0:13:24.89,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在企圖下色色的懲罰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一語中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.02,0:13:31.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我們看起像是那種人渣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.98,0:13:37.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家的面前 怎麼會提那種要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.53,0:13:40.95,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想玩那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.58,0:13:42.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.12,0:13:46.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下我就能合法地和哥哥親親我我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.33,0:13:50.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳奈想玩的話 我也參加吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.46,0:13:54.09,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偽裝成懲罰游戲 我就能和由佳奈擦出火花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這沒問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.97,0:13:57.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.09,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好誒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.09,0:14:03.81,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就玩國王游戲咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.98,0:14:13.69,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王 報上名來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.49,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好誒 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.70,0:14:18.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.53,0:14:19.57,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.66,0:14:24.62,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那表情是有什麼詭計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准備下什麼色色的命令啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2號打5號的耳光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.75,0:14:33.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令很普通嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.96,0:14:37.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.38,0:14:41.30,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是2號 童貞君是5號對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.72,0:14:44.81,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.06,0:14:47.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.73,0:14:51.77,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭子你就不知輕重嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.77,0:14:53.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.86,0:15:00.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懲罰很普通嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.49,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.66,0:15:06.99,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前也說過了 萬事都有前戲嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.91,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就安心地看下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.29,0:15:15.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}喂 你們想干啥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.58,0:15:15.00,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 第二回合開始咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.13,0:15:17.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.17,0:15:20.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是國王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.42,0:15:25.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號用嬰兒語自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是互聯網辣妹...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.15,0:15:34.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是1號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.90,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開始咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.90,0:15:38.69,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩開了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.69,0:15:41.53,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的嬰兒語哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.45,0:15:48.99,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫香椎結衣 16歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.70,0:15:53.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀飯的東西是 溫柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.46,0:15:57.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.96,0:16:01.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣 超可愛滴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這個 還挺不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.22,0:16:04.34,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像聲優一樣 真可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.93,0:16:07.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.93,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點開始下一局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.93,0:16:12.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.44,0:16:15.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我是國王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.85,0:16:21.53,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼6號玩家 請擺出寫真雜志偶像的性感POSE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.49,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.49,0:16:26.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是6號哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.96,0:16:36.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 從這個位置看不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.08,0:16:39.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.88,0:16:42.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的銷魂POSE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.01,0:16:45.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩個西瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒說過讓解開衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.06,0:16:52.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一幅色眯眯的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.48,0:16:59.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦 因為是游戲呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.37,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我口渴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.45,0:17:10.62,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}喂 慎平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.78,0:17:11.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 寧音再來一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.78,0:17:11.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.95,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}差不多可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也吃點點心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.62,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}時機已到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在說啥悄悄話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.17,0:17:23.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一局你就能和八女同學接吻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.59,0:17:29.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 你看我拿的筷子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠的筷子放高 近的筷子放低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.52,0:17:38.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就會從高的筷子開始抽起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.98,0:17:44.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 我就會成為下一局的國王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.32,0:17:47.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 也可以清楚誰是幾號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.82,0:17:50.74,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽不太清 但貌似挺厲害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.91,0:17:53.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 有一個艱巨的任務交給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.91,0:17:54.95,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你來分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王自己來分的話會被懷疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.54,0:18:01.09,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.09,0:18:03.09,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 景吾 給我們來一段吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.42,0:18:08.93,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠游戲和八女同學接吻 算哪回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.34,0:18:10.59,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.89,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他女生也要被那些笨蛋下手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼趕緊開始下一局吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.28,0:18:31.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.62,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 我是國王啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.12,0:18:44.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令 1號對國王 3號對2號深吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.55,0:18:47.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接 接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.97,0:18:53.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥倒是沒關系 和別人的話NG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.18,0:18:55.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以揍人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.93,0:18:57.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣實在不好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.31,0:18:59.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肅靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.27,0:19:03.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王的命令是絕對的 你們這些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.65,0:19:06.53,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 1號 2號 3號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手舉起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.32,0:19:13.62,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是3號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.91,0:19:16.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要和誰接吻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.87,0:19:18.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs35}國王命令 3號對2號舌吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.04,0:19:21.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個二五仔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.17,0:19:23.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.75,0:19:29.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓她們落入你們這群肮髒的東西手裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.72,0:19:33.34,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 我甘願犧牲自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.05,0:19:33.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs35}1號對國王舌吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.80,0:19:37.81,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.35,0:19:40.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻 接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.85,0:19:44.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起司 起司 起司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.69,0:19:48.53,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳奈 國王大人的命令是怎麼來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.44,0:19:52.91,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得好像說是絕對的什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 羽柴同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.41,0:19:58.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個男子漢一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.58,0:20:09.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起司 起司 起司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.55,0:20:19.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好玩了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多點人一起玩好像也不賴嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.77,0:20:26.69,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 也看到了難得的場面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.81,0:20:27.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.98,0:20:33.65,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是為了拯救大家 付出的代價也太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.95,0:20:36.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你幫了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.03,0:20:40.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人們的接吻可不常見 難得的經驗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和哥哥接吻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.37,0:20:47.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們倆 干嘛卿卿我我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.09,0:20:50.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.55,0:20:51.30,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.30,0:20:54.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說要暑假去哪裡玩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.80,0:20:58.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這裡的大伙一起出去玩肯定會很開心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.97,0:21:00.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.51,0:21:04.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的大伙一起出去玩肯定會留下不可磨滅的噩夢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.60,0:21:06.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你說這裡的大伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧 就這麼定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.11,0:21:11.57,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我想去海邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.57,0:21:16.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 調整一下日程 我應該也是可以去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.66,0:21:18.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去買新泳衣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}得鍛煉身體才行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.16,0:21:24.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}誰有12歲以下的妹妹呀 有的話請務必帶來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.82,0:21:21.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日旅游 還挺不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.71,0:21:29.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想去 可是為了改變形像已經沒錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒多少錢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.71,0:21:35.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家一起打工吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.26,0:21:40.93,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離暑假還有時間 旅行費用沒准能賺出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.97,0:21:46.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己賺錢去旅行超有趣的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.35,0:21:48.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.02,0:21:50.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.02,0:21:53.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家打工加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.58,0:23:26.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.66,0:23:27.54,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.54,0:23:28.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續兩集沒出場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.75,0:23:29.54,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.54,0:23:31.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正片大家都在開心地玩國王游戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.58,0:23:32.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.46,0:23:35.54,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是商量旅行的事情 由佳親都不叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.54,0:23:36.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.55,0:23:38.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心這集就只會說「就是說呀」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.05,0:23:39.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(635,530)\fad(300,0)}下回\N第一次的打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.46,0:23:39.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說呀
Comment: Marked=0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.95,0:01:37.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Like  自由なキミが好きだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.95,0:01:37.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like  雖然喜歡自由的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.63,0:01:42.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ほっとかれたらそれはそれでさみしい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.63,0:01:42.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果被冷落的話我會感到寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.41,0:01:47.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Love 「髪を切りすぎちゃったみたい」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.51,0:01:47.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love 「頭發好像剪得太短了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.03,0:01:49.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「ほんとだ」じゃない!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.03,0:01:49.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該說「是真的呢」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.87,0:01:53.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}そこは「でもかわいい」でしょ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.87,0:01:53.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要說「剪短也可愛呀」對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.00,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}そっと目を閉じたまま
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.00,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜靜閉上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.00,0:01:59.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}指先で探した
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.00,0:01:59.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用指尖去觸及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.45,0:02:04.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鍵と鍵穴みたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.45,0:02:04.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如鑰匙和鎖孔般默契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.99,0:02:07.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}そうだ この次のデート
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.99,0:02:07.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次的約會地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.59,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}わたしにまかせて!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.59,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來做決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.95,0:02:14.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}夏をプロデュースしたげる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.95,0:02:14.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏天制造最完美的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.58,0:02:16.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ふたりきりで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.58,0:02:16.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.78,0:02:17.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You are the First One!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.78,0:02:17.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一個!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.87,0:02:18.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.87,0:02:18.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.94,0:02:21.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ついにやってきましたマブしいSEASON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.94,0:02:21.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀的季節終於來臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.95,0:02:23.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.95,0:02:23.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}熱い太陽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎熱的太陽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.10,0:02:26.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}戀する気持ち もっと盛り上がってゆこう!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.10,0:02:26.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的心情讓我們再熱情高漲一點吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}こたえならYes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答自然是Yes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.19,0:02:28.93,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.19,0:02:28.93,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.23,0:02:32.07,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}だけどカンタンだって思われたくない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.23,0:02:32.07,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我並不想被人認為太容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.11,0:02:36.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}はじめては 一度だけ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.11,0:02:36.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次只有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.75,0:02:39.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大切に to you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.75,0:02:39.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要將自己完整地托付於你
Comment: Marked=0,0:03:14.78,0:03:16.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.60,0:22:03.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ヘナチョコ面に見せかけ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.60,0:22:03.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意裝成無能的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.32,0:22:05.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}案外やるときゃやる奴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.32,0:22:05.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的是個可靠的家伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}それでもちょこっと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又總是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.66,0:22:11.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}褒めれば調子に乗ってドジる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.66,0:22:11.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給點陽光就得意忘形弄巧成拙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.28,0:22:14.34,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ズタボロ破れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.28,0:22:14.34,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撕裂縱橫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.34,0:22:16.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}戀の傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.34,0:22:16.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.45,0:22:21.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}誰にも一生見せたくないけれど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.45,0:22:21.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明誰都不願意見到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.12,0:22:27.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}なぜだろ自然と會話してる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.12,0:22:27.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又情不自禁地說起了話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.84,0:22:30.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}なんだろな この感覚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.84,0:22:30.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢 這種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.44,0:22:33.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}あたたかい この安らぎ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.44,0:22:33.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖 感到安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.20,0:22:35.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}なんてことナイナイ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.20,0:22:35.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼的才沒有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.60,0:22:38.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}人生は甘くない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.60,0:22:38.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生可不甜美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.20,0:22:43.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}さあ 跪きなさい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.20,0:22:43.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 跪下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.80,0:22:46.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}あたしが好きならば!
